MR. SARCASTIC was away from the gate slowly, raced off the pace on the inside around the first turn and up the backstretch, began to improve position racing around the far turn, swung into the stretch in the five path and continued to gain ground to the wire. MARV'S MAGIC raced in the three path around the first turn, continued up the backstretch off the pace on the outside, began a bid from the four path headed into the far turn and flattened out in the stretch.
